[V2]
 Sit down to my table, turn on the TV
 Saw a whole lotta people worse of than me
 Folks living in cardboard houses I did not understand
 Poor little children still make lunch out of a back street garbage can
 One mama thew her arms up she 'why, why, why, why?'
 Her child lay on the sidewalk cause the shooters just drove by

SOLO

